{
  "stem": "10699.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We want to get through to the children, or through to the teachers, or through to people sometimes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The question mark is can they follow us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I even said, after a few days in the camp, when I saw what was happening, I said, if I come out of that hell, and I want to tell people what I see here, if they don't believe me, I will understand.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said that right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a hell like there has never been a hell like that, and I hope there will never be a hell like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The message I would like to leave is [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I would like, first of all, that the revisionists shouldn't have their way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have today archives-- and archives from Russia, from Germany, from everywhere, which clearly show what Hitler had in mind.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have to bring that message forward.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And generations after generations, they should never forget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if we do forget, it can happen again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, as Primo Levi says, the good ones didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the worst came back, he says.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it wasn't-- I mean, the fittest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that everybody, not everybody-- I would hardly say-- I said some of us, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] some luck, perhaps, some luck that we left at the-- I left Auschwitz at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could have died in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I left for Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went to a factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The very few days, it wasn't as bad, then it got worse, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I kept-- I kept leaving camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But, in the meantime, hundreds died on the way every time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was meant to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sometimes say, why me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that's the question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why me?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
